            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The MINIBALL spectrometer is a high-resolution",
                "HPGe detector array consisting of 24 sixfold segmented",
                "crystals, characterized by good spatial and energy",
                "resolutions."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " the Si detector system T-REX consists of two",
                "compact disk(CD) detectors. The forward CD detector",
                "consists of two layers with 140 and 1500-mum respective",
                "thicknesses, used as a delta-E-E telescope in order to",
                "detect and identify light charged particles. The first",
                "layer is segmented into 16 annular rings and 24",
                "vertical strips, enabling determination of the",
                "scattering angles."
              ]
            }
          ],
